#. type: Title =
#: modules/ROOT/pages/communities.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Free software communities"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/communities.adoc:10
msgid ""
"There are many levels of participation in a free software project, and none "
"of them should be closed.  Apart from the development team, who are usually "
"hired for that purpose, other people might contribute on an occasional or "
"ongoing basis.  This chapter focuses on the more social aspects of how to "
"work in this kind of community which is created around these projects."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/ROOT/pages/communities.adoc:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Contributing to free software communities"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/communities.adoc:19
msgid ""
"The concept of contribution covers much more than the code.  It can also "
"consist in:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/communities.adoc:21
msgid "Translations"
msgstr ""

