#. type: quote
#: modules/ROOT/pages/communities.adoc:108 modules/ROOT/pages/communities.adoc:129 modules/ROOT/pages/communities.adoc:156 modules/ROOT/pages/communities.adoc:172 modules/ROOT/pages/communities.adoc:246
